welcome_message_body: Welcome to Cabanatuan City, where rich history, vibrant culture, and warm hospitality await you. Enjoy our delicious local cuisine, explore our historical landmarks, and immerse yourself in the charm of our city. We hope you have a memorable and enjoyable stay!
